data.description: Presenting a charming opportunity in the heart of Detroit, this 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence stands as a canvas ready for a transformation. Embraced by hardwood floors that create a warm and inviting atmosphere, this home features a spacious kitchen with ample room for a dining table, making it an ideal space for both daily living and entertaining. The bedrooms offer versatile possibilities, providing flexibility to adapt the space to suit individual needs. With a bit of care and attention, this property has the potential to become a haven of comfort and style. With excellent qualities, this home has the potential for transition. This residence invites those with a discerning eye and a flair for creativity to envision the possibilities and embark on a journey to bring out the latent charm within. Don't miss the chance to turn this house into a personalized haven, where each room becomes a testament to your unique style and preferences. Schedule your showing today!
